Acknowledgments

ArgentOS is built on the shoulders of excellent open-source work:

- pi-mono (https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono) by Mario Zechner (@badlogic)
  The agent runtime core that ArgentOS builds upon. pi-mono provides the
  foundational agent loop, session management, and tool execution framework.

- OpenClaw by Peter Steinberger
  The original fork point that gave ArgentOS its launching pad. OpenClaw's
  architecture informed early design decisions for the gateway, plugin system,
  and channel infrastructure.
